item.title: Minnesota Vikings Alternate, New York Giants Throwback Jerseys Leak
item.description: Former NFL wide receiver Antonio Brown's social media network leaked two more jerseys that will be worn this season, including a Minnesota Vikings alternate and New York Giants throwback design.

item.title: Denver Broncos Unveil New “Mile High” Uniforms, Revive Throwback Design
item.description: Although a series of leaks ruined the surprise, the Denver Broncos officially unveiled new uniforms on Monday morning, marking the first significant overhaul of their look in 27 years.
